{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/DebuggingGuide","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Debugging issues in applications using Lockman requires a different approach from traditional debugging due to the complexity of exclusive control. LockmanManager provides powerful debugging features for developers to monitor lock states and identify problems.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By utilizing appropriate debugging tools, you can efficiently identify and resolve lock conflicts, deadlocks, performance issues, and more."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"LockmanManager Debug Features","anchor":"LockmanManager-Debug-Features","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"text":"Enabling Debug Logs","anchor":"Enabling-Debug-Logs","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Lockman provides detailed lock operation logs:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Enable debug logs (only works in DEBUG builds)","LockmanManager.debug.isLoggingEnabled = true"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Log output example"}]},{"type":"text","text":":"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["✅ [Lockman] canLock succeeded - Strategy: SingleExecution, BoundaryId: process, Info: LockmanSingleExecutionInfo(actionId: 'startProcessButtonTapped', uniqueId: 7BFC785A-3D25-4722-B9BC-A3A63A7F49FC, mode: boundary)","","❌ [Lockman] canLock failed - Strategy: SingleExecution, BoundaryId: process, Info: LockmanSingleExecutionInfo(actionId: 'startProcessButtonTapped', uniqueId: 1EBA9632-DE39-43B6-BE75-7C754476CD4E, mode: boundary), Reason: Boundary 'process' already has an active lock","","⚠️ [Lockman] canLock succeeded with cancellation - Strategy: PriorityBased, BoundaryId: sync, Info: LockmanPriorityBasedInfo(...), Cancelled: 'backgroundSync' (uniqueId: 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000), Error: precedingActionCancelled"]},{"text":"Current Lock State Display","anchor":"Current-Lock-State-Display","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can display lock states in table format:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Display current lock state","LockmanManager.debug.printCurrentLocks()"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Output example","type":"text"}]},{"text":":","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["┌─────────────────┬──────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────┬─────────────────┐","│ Strategy        │ BoundaryId       │ ActionId\/UniqueId                    │ Additional Info │","├─────────────────┼──────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────┼─────────────────┤","│ SingleExecution │ CancelID.process │ startProcessButtonTapped             │ mode: boundary  │","│                 │                  │ 08CC1862-136F-4643-A796-F63156D8BF56 │                 │","├─────────────────┼──────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────┼─────────────────┤","│ PriorityBased   │ CancelID.sync    │ backgroundSync                       │ priority: .low  │","│                 │                  │ 987f6543-a21b-34c5-d678-123456789012 │ behavior: .rep..│","└─────────────────┴──────────────────┴──────────────────────────────────────┴─────────────────┘"]},{"text":"Format Options","anchor":"Format-Options","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can customize the display format:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Compact display (for narrow terminals)","LockmanManager.debug.printCurrentLocks(options: .compact)","","\/\/ Detailed display","LockmanManager.debug.printCurrentLocks(options: .detailed)","","\/\/ Custom format","let customOptions = LockmanManager.debug.FormatOptions(","    useShortStrategyNames: true,","    simplifyBoundaryIds: true,","    maxStrategyWidth: 15,","    maxBoundaryWidth: 20",")","LockmanManager.debug.printCurrentLocks(options: customOptions)"]},{"text":"Cleanup Feature","anchor":"Cleanup-Feature","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can reset problematic lock states:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Clean up all locks from all strategies","LockmanManager.cleanup.all()","","\/\/ Clean up locks only for specific boundary","LockmanManager.cleanup.boundary(CancelID.userAction)"]}]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Learn how to debug Lockman-related issues in your application."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman"]]},"metadata":{"title":"Debugging Guide","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"Lockman"}],"roleHeading":"Article"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"kind":"article","seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Essentials","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/GettingStarted","doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/BoundaryOverview","doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/Lock","doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/Unlock","doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/ChoosingStrategy","doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/Configuration","doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/ErrorHandling"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Essentials"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/lockman\/debuggingguide"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://Lockman/documentation/Lockman/ErrorHandling":{"kind":"article","type":"topic","role":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/ErrorHandling","title":"Error Handling","url":"\/documentation\/lockman\/errorhandling","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Learn about common error handling patterns in Lockman."}]},"doc://Lockman/docu